metadata.name: NEVER SAY NEVER
metadata.description:
You want to make God laugh, tell him your plans. You want to challenge life, tell it what you'll never do. Believe me, it will immediately throw up situations that will show you that it's better not to say the word "never. 

Life loves movement, flexibility, variety and fluidity.
For such it opens the doors of fantastic opportunities, and for the stubborn it builds walls of insurmountable obstacles. 

I will never do that...
I will never work with art...
I will never fall in love again," we say, and we fall head over heels in love...

You've definitely had it, you say "I never..." and then things happen.
